{
  "id": "69a849982aa78253f4843af1",
  "title": "WSL2 Ubuntuにkeyringを入れる",
  "created": 1772636570,
  "updated": 1772639172,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a849982aa78253f4843af1",
      "text": "WSL2 Ubuntuにkeyringを入れる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636570,
      "updated": 1772636570
    },
    {
      "id": "69a853bf0000000000f05e99",
      "text": "[keyring]の入れ方",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772639167,
      "updated": 1772639172
    },
    {
      "id": "69a853bf0000000000f05e9a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772639167,
      "updated": 1772639167
    },
    {
      "id": "69a849990000000000f05e60",
      "text": " 1. インストールコマンドを入力",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636570,
      "updated": 1772636581
    },
    {
      "id": "69a849a40000000000f05e62",
      "text": "  $ sudo apt-get install gnome-keyring seahorse",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636581,
      "updated": 1772636618
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8499d0000000000f05e61",
      "text": "\t\tGUI管理ツールとして[seahorse]も入れる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636573,
      "updated": 1772636651
    },
    {
      "id": "69a849eb0000000000f05e64",
      "text": "\t\t\t[GitHub Copilot CLI]はこれ必須らしい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636652,
      "updated": 1772638030
    },
    {
      "id": "69a849ff0000000000f05e65",
      "text": "\t\t\t\thttps://github.com/github/copilot-cli/issues/49",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636672,
      "updated": 1772636672
    },
    {
      "id": "69a84a660000000000f05e6a",
      "text": "\t2. 下のコマンドを打っておく",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636776,
      "updated": 1772636785
    },
    {
      "id": "69a84a700000000000f05e6b",
      "text": "\t\t$ echo \"aaaaa\" | gnome-keyring-daemon --replace --unlock",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636785,
      "updated": 1772638120
    },
    {
      "id": "69a84a750000000000f05e6c",
      "text": "\t\t`echo \"aaaaa\"`は適当なダブらない文字列に変えてOK",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636789,
      "updated": 1772637095
    },
    {
      "id": "69a84fbd0000000000f05e73",
      "text": "\t\t\tてかこれ自体がパスワードの役割な気が…[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638142,
      "updated": 1772638150
    },
    {
      "id": "69a84a910000000000f05e6d",
      "text": "\t\t参考：https://tech.buty4649.net/entry/2023/01/31/182908",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636818,
      "updated": 1772636819
    },
    {
      "id": "69a849e20000000000f05e63",
      "text": "\t3. 自動的に起動するようにするのであれば、以下のコマンドをshellの起動スクリプトに放り込んでおく",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636642,
      "updated": 1772638229
    },
    {
      "id": "69a850140000000000f05e74",
      "text": "\t\tcode:bash",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638229,
      "updated": 1772638430
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8501e0000000000f05e75",
      "text": "\t\t echo \"aaaaa\" | gnome-keyring-daemon --unlock",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638239,
      "updated": 1772638247
    },
    {
      "id": "69a850c30000000000f05e77",
      "text": "\t\tログがうるさいので下のようにしてもいいかも",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638404,
      "updated": 1772638416
    },
    {
      "id": "69a850d20000000000f05e78",
      "text": "\t\tcode:bash",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638418,
      "updated": 1772638432
    },
    {
      "id": "69a850d20000000000f05e79",
      "text": "\t\t echo \"aaaaa\" | gnome-keyring-daemon --unlock 2> /dev/null",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638418,
      "updated": 1772638424
    },
    {
      "id": "69a84a410000000000f05e69",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636737,
      "updated": 1772636737
    },
    {
      "id": "69a84a030000000000f05e66",
